## Limitations
This report is limited by the availability of data up to October 2023 and does not include more recent developments or studies. Additionally, the sources used may have inherent biases, and the report does not cover every possible perspective on the issue. Further research could provide a more comprehensive understanding of the evolving public opinion and legislative changes regarding gun ownership rights.